%N A394319 a(n) = (2*n)! * [x^(2*n)] (C(x)'' - 2*x*C(x)' - C(x)) / 2, where C(x) satisfies C(x) = cosh( Integral C(x)^3 dx ).
%H A394319 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A394319/b394319.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..215</a>
%F A394319 a(n) = A394318(n,1).
%e A394319 C(x)   = 1 + x^2/2! + 13*x^4/4! + 493*x^6/6! + 37369*x^8/8! + ...
%e A394319 C(x)'  =       x/1! + 13*x^3/3! + 493*x^5/5! + 37369*x^7/7! + ...
%e A394319 C(x)'' =       1    + 13*x^2/2! + 493*x^4/4! + 37369*x^6/6! + ...
%e A394319 (C(x)'' - 2*x*C(x)' - C(x)) / 2 = 4*x^2/2! + 188*x^4/4! + 15480*x^6/6! + 2048488*x^8/8! + ...
